column5: Another year of soft water is over..   I bought a new tip up yesterday to look forward to winter.
That's horrifying.   Do the mods allow pics like that on this site ?
isnt "Gypsy's Place" an oxy ? kinda like Jumbo Shrimp or Military Intelligence
Wait...why did you put it into hybernation? A boat isn't a bear...you must cherish it, seize the day....can I have some change so I can go get loaded?!  Sad to see indeed..
I put mine away today too.  Where did you get the 2 stands for the back of the trailer? Homemade? They look solid.
Same here. Went to bed on Sat.
Yes they are homemade, just 2x4's and 3" screws.. Here's a pic from last year before they were painted.. Also you can see the skeleton under the tarp.
Thanks for the pic, I like the way the stands fit around the trailer frame.
